39:31.107 --> 39:32.195
Hey.

39:34.197 --> 39:35.721
Whoa, whoa, whoa.
Slow down. Slow down.

39:36.852 --> 39:39.464
Dead? What do you mean dead?

39:40.508 --> 39:43.946
No, that's-- that's impossible.

