<i>♪ Now I'm swaying alone ♪</i>

39:50.431 --> 39:53.913
<i>♪ I keep waiting for the call ♪</i>

39:53.913 --> 39:57.220
<i>♪ To see you fight,
to see you fight ♪</i>

39:57.220 --> 39:59.092
<i>♪ But you're never gonna call ♪</i>

39:59.092 --> 40:00.963
I should have taken
Collier's call more seriously.

40:02.487 --> 40:04.532
I could've
checked on him sooner.

40:04.532 --> 40:07.361
He said he was better.
I can't believe he's gone.

40:09.668 --> 40:11.887
With everything
that's happened and now this?

